## Why this exists

Most cloud comparisons are written for engineers. This one is written for sellers, sales engineers, and anyone who needs to hold a credible conversation with a VP Engineering, CTO, or CFO about cloud infrastructure decisions.

Understanding the landscape your buyer lives in — their cloud provider, their governance challenges, their FinOps pressure — is the difference between a vendor conversation and a strategic one.
